Dialogs.Dialog: Is this your first time here？ I'm getting excited.
Yeah. I think we'll enjoy it.
We're here again. Hehe... I want to play a lot today.
Yeah. Let's enjoy it to the fullest.
Geez, let's play as much as we can.
Knot 30 was fun. Let's try it again.
I'm pretty sure Knot 30 had some sort of winning formula, don't you？
Yeah, I'm sure it's a thing we have to try before.
It's fun to see Daruma-san fall at my age.
When Daruma-san falls, two types of people appear: those who go forwards and backward, and those who wait behind.
Ah, I know what I mean.
Yeah, it was fun. If it was for guidance, Rinko would probably be better at it.
Watermelon, in case you don't know, is a veggie... Rinko doesn't care either way as long as it tastes good.
Catching marshmallows was harder than I thought it would be. That's why I was so enthusiastic about it.
I heard that marshmallows can be eaten in many different ways. They also have collagen in them, so I heard they're good for your beauty.
Darts takes a lot of concentration. The better you get at it, the more addicted you might become！
There are many rules for darts. I guess it's more fun if you know them well.
I'd start with score calculation. I know it sounds like a lot of work, but you can do it...
Speed is so annoying. They both look so desperate.
Haha, that's how funny it is.
There are also local rules for speed. It's really complicated, so they should be unified.
Yeah, that happens in other games too.
Why are soap bubbles so soothing？
Kids and adults are the same in this way.
I heard that if you put sugar or hyaluronic acid in soap when you make it, it's harder for it to crack.
This looks so easy when you watch it on TV, but it's so hard when you try it yourself.
It's so exciting it keeps you on the edge of your seat.
I heard that guy who came up with game is some famous guy, right？ Did you know that？
This game is so simple, why do I get so excited about it？
Doesn't this look like it's just flirting when they're doing this as a couple？
Space Agents, huh... it was interesting. I'll keep it in mind.
These games are like the basics of arcade games, aren't they？
It's hard to have them at home.
I was caught off guard thinking I was just picking a panel. It takes a lot of thinking.
Maybe you need both math and intuition.
If you can connect the panels well, you can brag about it.
When you have 2 choices... you're at a loss.
Yeah, that's where the brains come in.
Ah, geez... I had a chance at the jackpot.
The moment you win the jackpot is a pleasant feeling, isn't it？ It seems to be addictive.
I was on the edge of my seat, and it seemed like a long time before the spinning stopped.
Grand Cross was fun, wasn't it？ Isn't there something more tricky？
You seem to be good at finding stuff like that, ▲小早川＊▲.
I didn't think I'd be that thrilled when I had the jackpot chance.
Yeah. It's a shame we lost it.
That was an awesome jackpot at the Grand Cross！ I was so excited I wanted to celebrate.
I really want to try it as many times as I can.
That was interesting. Doesn't Fortune Trinity feel like a bit of a trip？
You can see many different world heritage sites.
I thought for sure I could hit the jackpot！
"My hand are sweating！" Or so you said.
I really like the Fortune Trinity jackpot. I like the way the medals come out to the sound.
I'd love to see them again.
Aren't the animas in Animalotta cute？ I think Rinko likes the cat-like ones the best.
I really thought I could get the jackpot chance in Animalotta. The number of balls was amazing.
I'm glad I got the jackpot of Animalotta. I'm also satisfied with the beautiful performance.
Jackpot chances are a bit of a hassle, aren't they？
Even if you don't get it, you can still have fun just watching the performance.
I wish I had saved that jackpot chance... Too bad.
I'm sure it'll be okay next time.
Did you see the moment when the jackpot was decided？ I was so happy, I think I'll dream about it.
Me too！ It's burned into my memory.
When you win a jackpot, you want to brag about it out loud.
Yeah. That was kind of impressive.
Rinko likes medal games because they are unique to arcade games.
Medal games can be a lot of fun. I like gaming, but I think I'll get into this one.
I think you'll get more addicted to arcade games.
It was a great harvest. I got a lot of medals, and the production was sparkling and spectacular.
I wish it was always like this.
I didn't get many medals, but the game was fun.
Yeah. If we get a bunch of medals for that one, I'll have no complaints.
It was really fun. Rinko had a great time, how about you？
I got too carried away. Do you think Rinko got overzealous？
That's not true. I was hooked on it, too.
Time flies really fast, doesn't it？ I can't believe it's already over.
Yeah. I wish I could play more.
It's been great. I wish I could live here. Hehe.
Ah, it was fun. I'm sure it's because I'm with you that I'm having so much fun.
Haha, that's a nice thing to say.
Rinko is addicted now. I'll definitely come back again.
Hey, when are we coming next？ As soon as possible, I hope.
But... I was a little disappointed. I'll get my revenge next time！
I don't think Rinko is satisfied with these results.
You know, if I'd worked harder here.... I'll do some research when I get back.
I guess it's silver, but I want to guess it exactly.
Whoa！ I obtained a gold scratch without failing.
Oh, platinum！ I'm going for the big one.
This is... the legendary premium！？ That's kind of divine.
I feel it's on the left...
Hmm, I don't know. I'll leave it to you！
Yeah！ I'm glad I followed your advice, ▲小早川＊▲.
Alright！ Maybe your thoughts got through me, ▲小早川＊▲.
I should have trusted your intuition this time, ▲小早川＊▲...
